title: Making a (glossy) magazine in Adobe InDesign
description:
In this pack, you&#039;ll find Lynda.com video tutorials which explain how to make a (glossy) magazine. Also all the files are included, so that you can rebuild the template to your own magazine.

It is possible to start your own magazine on the papersize of your choice, like A4. After making this you can import all the styles, the video tutorial will explain how to do this.

Enjoy! Foppe
